OL,3,CDate confirmed for the banning of
OL,4,Cdisposable vapes
OL,6,FSingle-use vapes are set to be banned
OL,7,Ffrom 1 June, 2025 in Wales.
OL,9,FIt comes as the Welsh Government
OL,10,Fannounced its plans to tackle "litter
OL,11,Fand plastic pollution" and "protect"
OL,12,Fcommunities.
OL,14,FThe new regulations would prohibit the
OL,15,Fsupply of single-use vapes in a
OL,16,F"crucial step" towards waste reduction.
