OL,6,FIn a statement, Deputy First Minister
OL,7,Fand Cabinet Secretary for Climate
OL,8,FChange and Rural Affairs Huw Irranca-
OL,9,FDavies MS said: "The Welsh Government
OL,10,Fhas worked closely with UK Government
OL,11,Fand other Devolved Governments on this
OL,12,Fmatter and anticipate aligning our
OL,13,Fcoming into force dates.
OL,15,F"This will enable the bans to be
OL,16,Fimplemented in a co-ordinated manner
OL,17,Fto ensure high levels of compliance
OL,18,Fand consistent approach to enforcement
OL,19,Facross the UK.
