OL,6,F"Action to tackle the environmental
OL,7,Fand social impacts of single-use vapes
OL,8,Fis a key priority for the Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment and we continue to work
OL,10,Fwith the other UK nations to address
OL,11,Fthese challenges."
OL,13,FThe Welsh Government had initially
OL,14,Fintended for the ban to come into
OL,15,Feffect as of 1 April 2025, giving
OL,16,Fbusinesses "necessary time to prepare."
OL,18,FThe updated enforcement date of 1
OL,19,FJune, 2025 is expected to align with
OL,20,Fother UK nations to ensure a smoother
OL,21,Frollout of the ban.
