OL,3,CDate confirmed for the banning of
OL,4,Cdisposable vapes
OL,6,FAdult vaping in Wales has reached an
OL,7,Fall-time high of 11% according to
OL,8,Fpublic health charity Action on
OL,9,FSmoking and Health Wales (Ash Wales).
OL,10,FThis is compared to 8% in the 2023
OL,11,Fsurvey.
OL,13,FThey also revealed 80% of adults in
OL,14,FWales want to see a ban on the
OL,15,Fimportation and sale of disposable
OL,16,Fvapes.
