OL,4,Cdisposable vapes
OL,6,FEarlier in the year, the Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment explained: "Over 360
OL,8,Fmillion such vapes are bought each
OL,9,Fyear in the UK, with valuable and
OL,10,Fcritical materials such as lithium and
OL,11,Fcopper regularly being binned that
OL,12,Fcould instead be powering nearly 5,000
OL,13,Felectric vehicles."
OL,15,FHowever, the reasons behind the ban
OL,16,Fare not only environmental.
OL,18,FThe number of children and young
OL,19,Fpeople who vape has also surged with
OL,20,Fexperts calling for action.
