OL,6,FCommenting on the Welsh Government's
OL,7,Fannouncement, Children's Commissioner
OL,8,Ffor Wales Rocio Cifuentes MBE said:
OL,9,F"'Children are coming to secondary
OL,10,Fschool from primary schools addicted
OL,11,Fto vaping'- one of many highly
OL,12,Fconcerning things I've heard over the
OL,13,Fpast year in conversations with
OL,14,Fchildren and adults about vaping."
