OL,3,CDate confirmed for the banning of
OL,4,Cdisposable vapes
OL,6,FShe added: "I'm pleased today to see
OL,7,Fconfirmation that single-use vapes
OL,8,Fwill be banned in Wales, starting in
OL,9,FJune 2025. The Welsh Government must
OL,10,Fcontinue to use all its available
OL,11,Flevers to implement other important
OL,12,Fchanges recommended by Public Health
OL,13,FWales earlier this year. This includes
OL,14,Fproviding support for young people who
OL,15,Fare nicotine-dependent due to vapes,
OL,16,Frestricting flavours and flavour
OL,17,Fnames, and enforcing plain packaging
OL,18,Frules."
